        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>By quickly spinning your magnetic orb while channeling primal energy through it, you can create a tether of electricity that can pull objects and creatures across the battlefield, including yourself.</p>\n<p>You can cast @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.spells.Item.Electrotether] as a 3rd-rank primal innate spell twice per day, but the target becomes \"one creature, unattended object, or metal structure.\"</p>\n<p>If you target an unattended object, you immediately pull the object into your square and can grab the item if you have a free hand. If you target a metal surface, such as the side of a starship or building, you are immediately moved to the structure (this movement doesn't trigger reactions based on movement) and [[/act climb]].</p>"
